[gd_scene load_steps=6 format=3]

; Tuning gym. Every platform here is placed against the DEFAULT jump_height of
; 104 px, with the tallest step at 95 px — deliberately near the limit, so a
; sloppy jump misses and a good one lands. If you tune jump_height, expect the
; spacing to want adjusting with it.
;
; No pits and no death traps: falling always returns you to the floor. This room
; is for judging feel, not for punishing you while you judge it.

